{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715020/extras/directors-cut-gif.gif?t=1723618272\" /><br>We heard your feedback and we've been working for more than a year on this huge overhaul of our mechanics.<br><br><strong>DIRECTOR'S CUT FEATURES</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Twice as many weapons.<br></li><li> Cooldown based status effect Runes.<br></li><li> Merchant NPC.<br></li><li> Improved levels.<br></li><li> New / Improved enemies.<br></li><li> Translated world text (Region names, Items, Actions).<br></li><li> Improved bosses.<br></li><li> Improved combat (Hitboxes, Screen Shake and much more).<br></li><li> New sound design.</li></ul>And much more. Elden: Path of the Forgotten Director's Cut touches every element of the game. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715020/extras/Elden---Path-of-the-Forgotten-Temple.gif?t=1723618272\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715020/extras/Elden_Path_of_the_Forgotten_Promo_-_Description_-_600x120.png?t=1723618272\" /><br><br>Elden: Path of the Forgotten follows Elden\u2019s journey as they are thrust into a dark and dying world that they must survive. The story is inspired by my experiences leaving home at age of 15 and being thrust into a dark world that scared and confused me.<br><br>Guide Elden on a mission across a blighted land to save their mother from ancient horrors. Engage in brutal, technical combat and master eldritch magics as you walk the Forgotten Path. Elden explores non-traditional storytelling through indirect methods \u2013 like reading an illustrated book in a language you don\u2019t understand. The combat is based on reaction rather than action. Strategically, you will need to manage your stamina and position in order to master the art of parry or to find the perfect time to strike. Visually inspired by classic 16 and 8 bit games, Elden: Path of the Forgotten is a stunning, encapsulating, dark world waiting to be explored.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715020/extras/Elden-Item-Ques-v1.gif?t=1723618272\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715020/extras/Elden_Path_of_the_Forgotten_Promo_-_Features_-_600x120.png?t=1723618272\" /><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Figure out Elden\u2019s confusing world without guidance, tutorials, or support.<br></li><li>Many diverse and challenging regions.<br></li><li>Horrifying Lovecraftian enemies and bosses.<br></li><li>Unique and brutal weapons and spells.<br></li><li>Powerful and dynamic items.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715020/extras/OtherworldScene.gif?t=1723618272\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"You died","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/715020/a7fe4e4884982030438c9e1aa9ecea98681a3b66.jpg"},{"name":"Let them be forgotten","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/715020/1fb1203987403876a31784bdd5fc4f3d251e47b9.jpg"},{"name":"The old ones","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/715020/a50a4a98b8c6115abd7c7d8aef6538aae012f049.jpg"},{"name":"A touched mind","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/715020/f3aecc6bec4ba28a1e40aeba0f28981fe0d9b4e3.jpg"},{"name":"Channeling","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/715020/01cab9d4d8fd5befb723ee47078f2a630c5b0867.jpg"},{"name":"Not like this","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/715020/6186ff7f72c23f059bca975039768bbf9f5651b0.jpg"},{"name":"Monstrosity","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com